---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Filce.uk" description="Sam Filce is a telecoms professional and hobbyist tinkerer based in the UK. He writes honest reviews of the tech and gear he actually buys." canonicalPath="/about/">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container about-container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>About</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content prose">
        <p class="about-lead">Hey - I'm Sam. I work in telecoms by day and spend my evenings and weekends pulling apart gadgets, setting up servers, and generally acquiring more gear than is probably sensible.</p>

        <p>I started this site because I got tired of reviews written by people who'd had a product for 48 hours before a press embargo lifted. Everything here is stuff I've actually bought with my own money, lived with for a while, and formed a proper opinion on.</p>

        <h2>What I write about</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Home Automation</strong> - Mostly Home Assistant, smart switches, sensors and the occasional rabbit hole that ate my entire weekend</li>
          <li><strong>Homelabs</strong> - Self-hosted services, NAS boxes, mini PCs, networking gear</li>
          <li><strong>3D Printing</strong> - Printers, filament, mods and the prints that actually turned out useful</li>
          <li><strong>Photography & Video</strong> - Cameras, lenses, lighting, stabilisers - whatever I'm currently obsessing over</li>
          <li><strong>Tools & Home Renovation</strong> - Power tools, hand tools, anything that makes DIY less painful</li>
          <li><strong>Gaming Accessories</strong> - Controllers, headsets, peripherals - the stuff that actually makes a difference</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>The deal with affiliate links</h2>
        <p>Some links on this site are Amazon affiliate links. If you click through and buy something, I get a small commission - at no extra cost to you. I only link to things I'd actually recommend. I never write a post just to sell something.</p>

        <p>I'm registered with the Amazon Associates programme and comply with all applicable UK advertising regulations. Every post with affiliate links will say so clearly.</p>

        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>Found something useful here? Got a question about a product I've reviewed? You can reach me at <a href="mailto:sam@filce.uk">sam@filce.uk</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
